gnostr-signer (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Features:
    - GTK4/libadwaita GUI for identity management
    - D-Bus interface for Nostr signing operations (NIP-55L)
    - NIP-46 remote signer (bunker) support
    - Secure key storage via GNOME Keyring/libsecret
    - Application permission management
    - NIP-04 and NIP-44 encryption support

 -- GNostr Project <gnostr@example.com>  Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
